column6: Marvel's gothic gunslinger goes face-to-face with not one, but two stars of ANNIHILATION! Who has imprisoned Wraith, who is his fellow inmate, and who is their interrogator?!
column8: | letterer:Randy Gentile | colorist:Gina Going | writer:Javier Grillomarxuach | inker:Kyle Hotz | penciller (cover):Clint Langley
